-- Soros Says He’s Among ‘Angels’ Who Want Civilization to Survive
-- B y   T o n y   C z u c z k a
-- 2012-01-27T11:47:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-27/soros-says-he-s-among-angels-who-want-civilization-to-survive.html
Billionaire investor  George Soros 
said he’s “now on the side of the angels” who believe that
financial markets have a responsibility to preserve human
civilization.  “I really think it matters for all of us, for humanity,
for hedge-fund managers as other human beings, that our
civilization should survive,” Soros said in an interview with
Bloomberg Television’s  Erik Schatzker  in Davos, Switzerland,
today. “I am right now on the side of the angels. Not an easy
role to play.” Soros said he is among those “trying to keep
the system together.”  in trying to keep the global financial system and together.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
